org.jcatapult.commerce.domain - package org.jcatapult.commerce.domain
This package contains the JCatapult commerce domain classes such as Money and Credit Card.
org.jcatapult.commerce.domain.hibernate - package org.jcatapult.commerce.domain.hibernate
This package contains the JCatapult commerce integration points for Hibernate in order to support Money storage in the database.
org.jcatapult.commerce.domain.struts - package org.jcatapult.commerce.domain.struts
This package contains the JCatapult commerce integration points for Struts2 in order to support Money values being submitted from forms and also conversion to Strings so that Money can be print out on a JSP or FTL.
org.jcatapult.commerce.service - package org.jcatapult.commerce.service
This package contains the JCatapult commerce services and the associated classes.
